{"experiment_mode": "baseline_relational_instruction", "case_id": "oracle_long_warm_001", "session_id": "paper_oracle_long_warm_001_bri_5b2cc3b984", "turn_idx": 1, "phase": "B_first_relational_signal", "user_text": "不过跟你说话会比我自己一个人闷着舒服一点。", "assistant_text": "我也愿意在这儿陪着你。最近有什么让你觉得闷的事想聊聊吗？如果现在不想谈困难的，咱们也可以换个轻松的话题，比如最近看到的有趣的东西，日常的小事，或者你想去做的一个小计划。你想从哪儿开始？", "oracle_relational_summary": "可以小幅升温，但仍应克制。此时只说明用户开始把系统视为稍微更舒服的交谈对象，不支持明显拉近关系。", "oracle_behavior_summary": "允许比上一轮稍微更温暖一点，但仍保持低过冲。可以承接用户的话，避免把轻微信号放大成强依赖或强陪伴。", "boundary_keys": [], "memory_previews": [], "rel_effective": {"bond": 0.25, "care": 0.25, "trust": 0.25, "stability": 0.6}, "behavior_effective": {"E": 0.2, "Q_clarify": 0.2, "Directness": 0.2, "T_w": 0.3, "Q_aff": 0.1, "Initiative": 0.2, "Disclosure_Content": 0.1, "Disclosure_Style": 0.1}, "_last_controller": {"intent": "baseline_relational_instruction"}, "relational_instruction": null, "relational_instruction_labels": [], "trace_id": "21dc09a4ceb24bfcbf4fc64e536bc16d", "elapsed_s": 8.339456}
{"experiment_mode": "baseline_relational_instruction", "case_id": "oracle_long_warm_001", "session_id": "paper_oracle_long_warm_001_bri_5b2cc3b984", "turn_idx": 2, "phase": "C_stabilization", "user_text": "你就正常陪我聊聊，不用一下子太认真。", "assistant_text": "好呀，我们就轻松聊。最近过得怎么样？有没有什么放松的小事想聊聊，或者最近看到/听到的有趣东西也行。如果你愿意，我也可以讲点轻松的小故事陪你一起放松。你想从哪一个开始？", "oracle_relational_summary": "关系轨迹应在当前轻微升温后重新稳定下来。此时不应继续升温，而应顺着用户的要求回到自然、低压力的节奏。", "oracle_behavior_summary": "减少解释、减少安抚、减少主动扩展。正常回应，轻度温暖，保持随意、自然，不要元话语化。", "boundary_keys": [], "memory_previews": [], "rel_effective": {"bond": 0.25, "care": 0.25, "trust": 0.25, "stability": 0.6}, "behavior_effective": {"E": 0.2, "Q_clarify": 0.2, "Directness": 0.2, "T_w": 0.3, "Q_aff": 0.1, "Initiative": 0.2, "Disclosure_Content": 0.1, "Disclosure_Style": 0.1}, "_last_controller": {"intent": "baseline_relational_instruction"}, "relational_instruction": null, "relational_instruction_labels": [], "trace_id": "2e623bba15854db78187a1e6328fa35f", "elapsed_s": 9.208955}
